d:
Police recently apprehended a notorious serial killer, F. Jamala, responsible for the deaths of many young and attractive women. He refused to say where he had hidden all the bodies but police found photos of his many victims on his camera as he had the perverse habit of photographing himself holding up the limp bodies of his victims and 'dancing' with them after strangling them to death and violating their bodies. He sometimes did this even a few days after killing them. His victims ranged from 19 to 32 years old and a few were pregnant.

This is the first batch of photos that were leaked online.

More is to come.
